{{div col end}}}}
{{term|term=drug prohibition |content=[[drug prohibition]]}}
{{defn|Laws in some jurisdictions banning the cultivation or sales of plants including [[cannabis]], [[opium poppy]], and [[psilocybin mushroom]]s in an attempt to prevent their use. These bans are criticized because they create a black market and because enforcement is disproportionate in communities of color.<ref name="DrugWarCrimes"/><ref name="NewJimCrow"/>}}
{{term|term=drug war or Drug War |content=drug war or Drug War}}
{{defn|Term referring to wars fought over control of drug commerce, including the 19th Century [[Opium Wars]], and contemporary police and military operations including the [[Mexican War on Drugs]], the [[Philippine Drug War]], and the [[War on drugs|U.S. War on Drugs]].}}

{{glossary end}}

