== O ==
{{glossary}}
{{term|term=oil |content=oil}}
{{defn|Slang name for [[hash oil]], a resin extracted from cannabis.<ref name=DEA/> [See [[cannabis edible]]s and extracts.]}}
{{term|term=oil rig |content=oil rig}}
{{defn|A water filter modified for vaporizing [[hash oil]].<ref name="DenverPostCannabist">{{cite web | url=http://www.thecannabist.co/2016/03/03/5-dabbing-essentials-marijuana-concentrates/45058/ | title=Dabbing essentials: the best dab rigs and gear | work=[[The Denver Post]] | date=March 3, 2016 | accessdate= | author=Prichard, Ry}}</ref>}}
